title: Real GDP of Washington , by industry 2018

summary: This chart shows the Real GDP in Washington .
It shows Government_and_government_enterprises was the Real at just 0.65 degrees and Professional_and_business_services was the warmest at 83.45 value .

After Government_and_government_enterprises , the next Real GDP are Finance_insurance_real_estate_rental_and_leasing at 83.45 degrees , followed by Mining_quarrying_and_oil_and_gas_extraction at 18 degrees , Information at 72.82 degrees and then Manufacturing at 59.03 degrees .
